{"tid":1850420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今朝有沙田手足做嘢點解無人講？","createTime":"2020-01-29T13:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T15:54:09.000Z","uid":343080,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6f5a9fe1977541073113372c7c52aade118857","tid":1850420,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"今日朝早嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎明抗疫</span></span>行動<br />\n因為啲狗一早部署定啲狗力係各區 <br />\n所以有手足被咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實沙田嘅手足嘅行動尚算成功<br />\n附上今朝嘅片段<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">因為揾唔到其他片 所以用住狗fb嘅片段先 </span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1SwY3WaQM4mlb6vK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1SwY3WaQM4mlb6vK&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHwy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=859b0b9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1SwY3WaQM4mlb6vK</a><br />\n<br />\n其實依類行動比起<br />\n一早講晒時間地點比狗部署可能會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其他手足亦可以參考番今朝沙田手足嘅做法<br />\n一齊進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n今朝嘅行動亦證明咗場運動係無靜止左<br />\n勇武手足一直默默咁做梗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後多謝所有手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人支持醫護罷工</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求政府 立即封關</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fa557234912b15b781a1d9266cb1d0e3f65740cb","tid":1850420,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac6f5a9fe1977541073113372c7c52aade118857","tid":1850420,"uid":343080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"今日朝早嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黎明抗疫</span></span>行動<br />\n因為啲狗一早部署定啲狗力係各區 <br />\n所以有手足被咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但其實沙田嘅手足嘅行動尚算成功<br />\n附上今朝嘅片段<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">因為揾唔到其他片 所以用住狗fb嘅片段先 </span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://fbwat.ch/1SwY3WaQM4mlb6vK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffbwat.ch%2F1SwY3WaQM4mlb6vK&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBHwy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=859b0b9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fbwat.ch/1SwY3WaQM4mlb6vK</a><br />\n<br />\n其實依類行動比起<br />\n一早講晒時間地點比狗部署可能會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">其他手足亦可以參考番今朝沙田手足嘅做法<br />\n一齊進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n今朝嘅行動亦證明咗場運動係無靜止左<br />\n勇武手足一直默默咁做梗嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後多謝所有手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港人支持醫護罷工</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求政府 立即封關</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-